tv.amwa.maj.exception

Interface NewForMAJ

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DuplicateEssenceKindException, DuplicateException, DuplicatePackageIDException, DuplicateParameterException, GenerationMethodNotSupportedException, InstanceOverflowException, NotImplementedException, RationalRangeException

    public interface NewForMAJ

    This interfaces labels new exceptions introduced for this Java implementation of the AAF class model. An exception implementing this interface does not have an AAF_RESULT code with a similar sounding name in the C-based AAF SDK.
